    "description": "Cand3ce...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn a galaxy on the brink of war, only the chosen one can save us all...<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJoin Candice, Krystal, and all of their friends and frenemies, on their turn-based trans-galactic RPG tryst through the tempests of time, across seven planets.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBoost your abilities as Candice with the Brandi Sisters' treatments, or steal them from your enemies as Krystal. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nWin over friends and civilisations in this ticking timebomb to all-out destruction. Discover ancient, dark secrets, and unleash scandalous romances while hurtling through space itself.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLevel up, and save us all from their greatest challenge yet!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n...Cand3ce... a brand new me...<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* A 10-20 hour turn-based RPG epic<br />\r\n* Find out the shocking truth behind Candice, in this finale to the web of secrets spun throughout the first two games<br />\r\n* A tantalisingly tangy soundtrack<br />\r\n* Status effects that are actually worth using<br />\r\n* Voluptuous voice acting<br />\r\n* A variety of beetle-based sidequests<br />\r\n* A modicum of romance<br />\r\n* Sensationally trick throughout",
